31:23.507 --> 31:26.050
And today I, Claude, from France,

31:26.051 --> 31:28.303
want to pay you back
for the hospitality

31:28.304 --> 31:29.637
you have shown me,

31:29.638 --> 31:31.764
to thank not just
the Wilson family.

31:31.765 --> 31:33.766
Give them a hand.

31:33.767 --> 31:35.727
There they are.

31:35.728 --> 31:38.646
Very nice.

31:38.647 --> 31:41.816
Cassidy, please,
don't get hooked on me.

31:41.817 --> 31:44.819
Choose one of the many
idiot boys in this town.

31:44.820 --> 31:47.071
And, Kevin, I like you.
I really do.

31:47.072 --> 31:48.990
Put down that stupid dummy.

31:48.991 --> 31:52.761
You will never get girls as
long as you have that thing.

31:54.079 --> 31:56.581
Anyway, I am so
grateful to all of you

31:56.582 --> 31:59.417
that I have decided to
present you with a gift,

31:59.418 --> 32:02.712
much as you Americans were
given the Statue of Liberty

32:02.713 --> 32:04.631
by my country of France-

32:04.632 --> 32:06.883
France being the place
I am from and no place else.

32:06.884 --> 32:10.094
Here it is!

32:10.095 --> 32:12.847
Hey, that's just Big Rock Rock.

32:12.848 --> 32:14.682
Hmm.
Yes...

32:14.683 --> 32:17.560
But thanks to my
talents in explosives,

32:17.561 --> 32:20.229
talents which I learned
along with every other

32:20.230 --> 32:23.399
French school boy in France,
the land of my birth,

32:23.400 --> 32:25.401
I present to you...

32:25.402 --> 32:29.339
Mount America Foreverberg!

32:32.534 --> 32:36.287
These are your four
greatest American icons-

32:36.288 --> 32:39.207
billionaire wig model
Donald Trump...

32:39.208 --> 32:42.126
professional man-hater
Taylor Swift...

32:42.127 --> 32:45.588
tiny ageless weirdo Tom Cruise...

32:45.589 --> 32:50.093
and famed drug lord
Lance Armstrong!

32:50.094 --> 32:52.762
I'm getting a hankering
for the full-on salute.

32:52.763 --> 32:55.723
So you still do get those?

32:55.724 --> 32:58.226
Tom Cruise starred in
one of my favorite films,

32:58.227 --> 32:59.686
Jerry Maguire.

32:59.687 --> 33:01.896
I got misty when Renee
Zellweger dumped him.

33:01.897 --> 33:05.817
Thanks for the spoiler, jerk.
I haven't watched it yet.

33:05.818 --> 33:08.736
We love you!

33:08.737 --> 33:10.547
Way to go.
You're the best, Achmed.

33:11.323 --> 33:14.492
My American dream has come true.

33:14.493 --> 33:17.996
I believe I can safely say,
with no fear of being

33:17.997 --> 33:20.415
ironically contradicted,
that nothing,

33:20.416 --> 33:23.543
I mean nothing, can ruin
this golden moment.

33:23.544 --> 33:26.754
Hello, Achmed.

33:26.755 --> 33:29.007
Holy crap.

33:29.008 --> 33:34.053
United States Americans,
my name is Hassan al-Hassan.

33:34.054 --> 33:35.888
Hey, that there's a terrorist.

33:35.889 --> 33:37.181
Nice going, Chet.

33:37.182 --> 33:38.933
Just because he has an Arabic name,

33:38.934 --> 33:41.019
he's automatically a terrorist.

33:41.020 --> 33:42.645
I am a terrorist.

33:42.646 --> 33:46.024
Welcome to America.

33:46.025 --> 33:48.484
This person is a traitor!

33:48.485 --> 33:52.947
Achmed's name isn't Claude.
Achmed's name is Achmed.

33:52.948 --> 33:54.073
It is?

33:54.074 --> 33:57.201
And he is a terrorist.
He is?

33:57.202 --> 33:59.203
And he is a skeleton.

33:59.204 --> 34:00.580
He is?

34:00.581 --> 34:02.665
A re r-re re-to n?
I am?

34:02.666 --> 34:06.478
Yeah, but if his name is
Achmed, then where's Claude?

34:14.469 --> 34:16.637
Is what he said true?

34:16.638 --> 34:18.473
No!
Well...

34:18.474 --> 34:22.018
No, no, no, I'm no terrorist.
I'm a nice guy.

34:22.018 --> 34:25.146
You know, the real me,
production-number me.

34:25.147 --> 34:26.438
Remember my song?

34:26.440 --> 34:28.065
Everything you know about me

34:28.067 --> 34:30.693
says I'm a great guy
and a true American.

34:30.694 --> 34:34.781
Everything except this!

34:34.782 --> 34:37.283
I found this in his room.

34:37.284 --> 34:39.284
All his plans to blow
us up are in here...

34:39.286 --> 34:43.039
and some weird drawings of
him riding a flying horse?

34:43.040 --> 34:46.083
It was a superhero character
I was working on-

34:46.085 --> 34:47.918
Turban Cowboy.

34:47.920 --> 34:49.629
It's turban time.

34:49.630 --> 34:52.983
Well, now that I
hear it out loud...

34:55.594 --> 34:57.053
Come on, guys.

34:57.054 --> 34:58.763
This is America,
where if you're white,

34:58.764 --> 35:00.598
you can get away with anything.

35:00.599 --> 35:03.493
And there's nobody whiter than me.

35:04.937 --> 35:06.604
I know him.
In my heart, it's not true.

35:06.605 --> 35:09.565
Crazy.
What about my reelection?

35:09.566 --> 35:11.734
I think he might be a terrorist.

35:11.735 --> 35:14.529
Please, I beg you. Listen to me.

35:14.530 --> 35:16.948
Are any of us what we
really appear to be?

35:16.949 --> 35:18.616
Daddy, maybe he is a terrorist.

35:18.617 --> 35:20.719
If you would only listen.

35:22.538 --> 35:24.306
Silence!
I kill you!

35:28.001 --> 35:32.463
Is what a real terrorist might say.

35:32.464 --> 35:35.842
I guess we should call the police.

35:35.843 --> 35:38.803
Not necessary. I'm a deputy.

35:38.804 --> 35:40.138
You bought that at a toy store.

35:40.139 --> 35:41.949
I didn't buy this at no toy store.

35:43.142 --> 35:44.851
I won it at a church raffle.

35:44.852 --> 35:47.913
Say your prayers, bonehead.

35:53.318 --> 35:56.529
This is FBI agent Jack Bauer.

35:56.530 --> 35:57.822
Ooh!

35:57.823 --> 35:59.574
Not the one from TV.

35:59.575 --> 36:01.784
Aw!

36:01.785 --> 36:04.245
It's my real name.
It's fairly common.

36:04.246 --> 36:07.165
I get this all the time. Calm down.

36:07.166 --> 36:11.895
You have 24 seconds to
surrender, starting now.

36:13.922 --> 36:16.841
Oh, no, I'm too pretty for prison.

36:16.842 --> 36:18.551
Yes, you are.

36:18.552 --> 36:20.178
Achmed, before you go,

36:20.179 --> 36:22.180
there's someone who
wants to say something.

36:22.181 --> 36:25.600
You're a "dad" man!
You should "de" ashamed.

36:25.601 --> 36:27.995
That toy is possessed
with a human spirit!

36:30.522 --> 36:34.275
Foot bones, don't fail me now!

36:34.276 --> 36:37.153
Stop it, Chet.
You're gonna hurt somebody.

36:37.154 --> 36:41.115
Freedom ain't free, Ev.

36:41.116 --> 36:42.909
Not so fast!

36:42.910 --> 36:45.953
I've got a Mexican,
and I'm not afraid to use it.

36:45.954 --> 36:47.914
I am not an "it."
My name is Carlos.

36:47.915 --> 36:49.540
This is not about you.

36:49.541 --> 36:52.477
Anybody makes a move,
and I blow him.

36:57.549 --> 37:00.218
With the leaf blower.

37:00.219 --> 37:02.386
I can't believe you all went there.

37:02.387 --> 37:04.055
I am so disappointed.

37:04.056 --> 37:06.992
Ah, screw it.

37:12.481 --> 37:16.400
Good-bye, Americaville.

37:16.401 --> 37:17.944
Hello, traitor.

37:17.945 --> 37:19.504
Hassan!

37:24.785 --> 37:28.913
It's day five of
"America Made to Look Stupid."

37:28.914 --> 37:32.041
The little town of Americaville
deals with the revelation

37:32.042 --> 37:35.461
that they've been harboring
the known terrorist Achmed

37:35.462 --> 37:37.755
who lived among them in disguise.

37:37.756 --> 37:39.507
Reaction to this story has come

37:39.508 --> 37:41.509
from across the political spectrum,

37:41.510 --> 37:43.386
with Democrats and Republicans

37:43.387 --> 37:45.930
finally finding common
ground on something.

37:45.931 --> 37:49.642
Americaville, now known
as Terrorist Town, USA,

37:49.643 --> 37:53.396
is the worst city in the
entire United States.

37:53.397 --> 37:54.897
It's a town of pinheads,

37:54.898 --> 37:56.357
and the biggest pinheads of all

37:56.358 --> 37:58.276
are the family that
harbored the terrorist.

37:58.277 --> 37:59.944
And they're the subject
of my new book,

37:59.945 --> 38:01.445
Killing the Wilsons.

38:01.446 --> 38:04.407
America is a country
of laws and due process,

38:04.408 --> 38:05.741
but in the Wilsons' case,

38:05.742 --> 38:07.868
a drone strike is
too good for them.

38:07.869 --> 38:09.495
Are we even sure

38:09.496 --> 38:11.376
that Mr. Wilson is the
father of this terrorist?

38:16.086 --> 38:17.586
Hmm?

38:17.587 --> 38:19.171
Automaker U.S. Motors,

38:19.172 --> 38:22.133
where terrorist harborer
Wayne Wilson once worked,

38:22.134 --> 38:24.885
announced today that, as
a gesture of apology,

38:24.886 --> 38:26.804
they will close their
Americaville plant,

38:26.805 --> 38:28.472
demolish it, burn the ruins,

38:28.473 --> 38:29.974
lock the ashes in a concrete vault,

38:29.975 --> 38:32.310
and bury the vault
under Giants Stadium.

38:32.311 --> 38:34.895
Would you mind if
we turned that off?

38:34.896 --> 38:37.398
Sorry. We're under orders
to make you watch it

38:37.399 --> 38:39.775
and keep TiVo-ing back
to the beginning.

38:39.776 --> 38:42.028
And they're the subject
of my new book,

38:42.029 --> 38:46.699
Killing the Wilsons.

38:46.700 --> 38:48.451
So that's your testimony.

38:48.452 --> 38:51.704
You had no idea this fella was
a terrorist or a skeleton?

38:51.705 --> 38:53.372
No, we just liked him.

38:53.373 --> 38:54.957
Okay, we're done here.

38:54.958 --> 38:56.667
Thank you.

38:56.668 --> 38:58.878
Maybe we can go back to some
version of our lives and-

38:58.879 --> 39:00.296
No, ma'am, you don't understand.

39:00.297 --> 39:02.524
I said we're done here.

39:07.179 --> 39:09.597
This is not the America
I grew up in.

39:09.598 --> 39:11.265
I advise you to be quiet.

39:11.266 --> 39:13.267
Anything you say may be
used against you at trial.

39:13.268 --> 39:15.644
Oh, there won't be a trial.

39:15.645 --> 39:17.330
Uh, no worries, then. Here we go.

39:21.485 --> 39:25.363
My friends,
today your new life begins,

39:25.364 --> 39:29.450
for just on the other side
of this tunnel is America

39:29.451 --> 39:33.537
and your new Home...
Depot parking lot.

39:33.538 --> 39:35.039
Yes!

39:35.040 --> 39:37.500
Oh, we are finally out
of that wretched place

39:37.501 --> 39:39.960
and away from those
horrible people.

39:39.961 --> 39:44.399
But you guys have fun.
Knock yourselves out.

39:49.971 --> 39:53.140
I can't believe the
Wilsons just gave me up

39:53.141 --> 39:55.142
after all we meant to each other.

39:55.143 --> 39:56.519
I broke bread with them.

39:56.520 --> 39:58.646
I put a bomb in their guest room.

39:58.647 --> 40:00.815
How could you let
yourself be brainwashed

40:00.816 --> 40:03.275
by those infidels, after
we spent so much time

40:03.276 --> 40:04.902
brainwashing you to hate them?

40:04.903 --> 40:07.738
I guess I am just washable.

40:07.739 --> 40:09.615
Soon this will all be over,

40:09.616 --> 40:12.785
and the decadent nation will
only be a bitter memory.

40:12.786 --> 40:15.621
Two tickets for the Third World,
please, first-class.

40:15.622 --> 40:17.915
May the Wilsons rot in hell!

40:17.916 --> 40:20.626
I am glad I will never
see them again.

40:20.627 --> 40:22.503
Wait. What's this?

40:22.504 --> 40:25.131
There we see the escaped
terrorist's accomplices

40:25.132 --> 40:26.424
being led away to prison.

40:26.425 --> 40:28.676
Terrorist lovers, go home!

40:28.677 --> 40:31.011
Go back to another country!

40:31.012 --> 40:32.638
They were not my accomplices.

40:32.639 --> 40:35.224
I was the mastermind
of this fiasco.

40:35.225 --> 40:36.892
If I could just say one thing...

40:36.893 --> 40:39.478
Claude, Achmed, wherever you are,

40:39.479 --> 40:41.689
if you can hear me...
I can!

40:41.690 --> 40:44.358
We know you're really a nice boy,

40:44.359 --> 40:47.837
and we hope you're okay.

40:49.406 --> 40:52.116
What?

40:52.117 --> 40:54.368
The Wilsons are put onto
the prison bus and...

40:54.369 --> 40:59.874
goooooooooal!

40:59.875 --> 41:02.585
I can't let the Wilsons become
the first innocent people

41:02.586 --> 41:04.795
ever wrongly imprisoned in America.

41:04.796 --> 41:07.298
Hassan, you must take me
back there to help them.

41:07.299 --> 41:08.883
You are insane.

41:08.884 --> 41:10.593
I wouldn't pay more
attention to the shrieks

41:10.594 --> 41:12.470
of a rabid water buffalo.

41:12.471 --> 41:15.097
Oh, yes, how is your wife?

41:15.098 --> 41:18.476
Zing, boom!
American put-down humor.

41:18.477 --> 41:21.061
For that, I should
kill until you are dead.

41:21.062 --> 41:23.564
But she is fine.
She's lost some weight.

41:23.565 --> 41:25.316
She's more cow than water buffalo.

41:25.317 --> 41:27.359
Anyway, come to your senses!

41:27.360 --> 41:30.946
Why do you want to go back to
that devil-filled country?

41:30.947 --> 41:33.073
All right, I will tell you.

41:33.074 --> 41:35.910
I want you to imagine a
place where all are equal

41:35.911 --> 41:39.330
and all are welcome, no
matter where you came from

41:39.331 --> 41:42.541
or who your father was or
how much land you own.

41:42.542 --> 41:45.836
It's a place dedicated to
the pursuit of happiness,

41:45.837 --> 41:49.298
where all the good things in
life are spread before you.

41:49.299 --> 41:53.260
And it is your right to take
as much as your heart desires.

41:53.261 --> 41:58.682
This place, my friend,
is called HomeBound Buffet.

41:58.683 --> 42:00.434
And America is filled with them.

42:00.435 --> 42:03.354
Loom

42:03.355 --> 42:07.775
These people-
they all seem so happy.

42:07.776 --> 42:10.945
That's what unlimited
buffet does for a nation.

42:10.946 --> 42:12.238
Unlimited?

42:12.239 --> 42:14.823
Surely there must be some limits.

42:14.824 --> 42:16.116
Nope.

42:16.117 --> 42:18.452
All right, they serve dinner, yes,

42:18.453 --> 42:20.663
but surely not desert.

42:20.664 --> 42:25.042
Bottomless frozen-yogurt bar
with all kinds of toppings-

42:25.043 --> 42:28.003
Oreo, Snickers, Cap'n Crunch.

42:28.004 --> 42:30.339
Don't say Butterfingers.
Don't say Butterfingers.

42:30.340 --> 42:32.216
Butterfingers.

42:32.217 --> 42:35.278
I must go there at once.

42:36.805 --> 42:39.306
Let me in!

42:39.307 --> 42:42.434
I must go to... Route 75, America,

42:42.435 --> 42:44.645
at the West Town
Country Mall at once.

42:44.646 --> 42:47.273
No! We have to save
the Wilsons first.

42:47.274 --> 42:49.900
Just a little fro-yo?
Okay.

42:49.901 --> 42:53.654
One standard serving of fro-yo,
no more than two toppings.

42:53.655 --> 42:54.756
Ooh, yay!

42:55.615 --> 42:56.782
Let us in!

42:56.783 --> 42:58.075
Hey, you.

42:58.076 --> 42:59.368
Get away from there.

42:59.369 --> 43:01.245
Holy crap. It's the po-po.

43:01.246 --> 43:04.081
That's the funny name they
have for police in America.

43:04.082 --> 43:05.499
I love it.

43:05.500 --> 43:08.210
I said get out of here. No entry!

43:08.211 --> 43:10.212
But we have to save our friends.

43:10.213 --> 43:12.339
The FBI thinks they are terrorists,

43:12.340 --> 43:13.841
but they're not.

43:13.842 --> 43:16.218
We are...

43:16.219 --> 43:18.804
is what a bad person would say

43:18.805 --> 43:21.390
in the scene from our
new Broadway musical,

43:21.391 --> 43:23.684
Les Mis Arabs.

43:23.685 --> 43:24.977
Uh, got to go!

43:24.978 --> 43:27.330
Terrorists! After 'em!

43:33.320 --> 43:36.822
Achmed, I am so sorry.
What do we do now?

43:36.823 --> 43:38.490
We do what Americans do.

43:38.491 --> 43:40.117
Eat?
No.

43:40.118 --> 43:42.745
What Americans do when
they run out of options.

43:42.746 --> 43:44.455
Throw a Hail Mary pass?

43:44.456 --> 43:46.206
Close. They pray.

43:46.207 --> 43:49.460
But we pray all the time,
like, 38 times a day.

43:49.461 --> 43:52.087
No, no, we have to
pray like Americans.

43:52.088 --> 43:53.672
How is that?

43:53.673 --> 43:56.050
They ask for things
like sports victories,

43:56.051 --> 43:59.053
no pregnancy, and
celebrity side boob.

43:59.054 --> 44:01.639
What do we pray for-side boob?

44:01.640 --> 44:03.366
No. A miracle.

44:11.858 --> 44:13.984
Aah!

44:13.985 --> 44:15.277
Side boob.

44:15.278 --> 44:17.338
Aah! Aah!

44:19.115 --> 44:20.616
It's American.

44:20.617 --> 44:23.160
Yes, bald eagle,
mighty American symbol,

44:23.161 --> 44:25.537
who is the second-place
choice after a turkey,

44:25.538 --> 44:27.998
take us into America.

44:27.999 --> 44:31.478
It's turban time!

45:07.080 --> 45:09.456
We have live team
coverage of the bus convoy

45:09.457 --> 45:11.875
as it slowly makes its way
down the main street

45:11.876 --> 45:14.712
of Americaville and
on to Guantanamo.

45:14.713 --> 45:17.172
Let's go now live to
our Madison Ashford,

45:17.173 --> 45:18.799
who's embedded with
the terrorist family

45:18.800 --> 45:20.718
and their captors.

45:20.719 --> 45:23.887
Dave, I'm here with the
terrorist sympathizers.

45:23.888 --> 45:26.932
We simply gave him a home.

45:26.933 --> 45:28.559
Confessed terrorist sympathizers

45:28.560 --> 45:30.894
as they head to their
well-earned imprisonment.

45:30.895 --> 45:34.732
There's no place like home.

45:34.733 --> 45:36.942
Another barrage of
eggs has hit the bus.

45:36.943 --> 45:39.278
That's why I'm in body armor.

45:39.279 --> 45:41.238
There's my Girl Scout leader

45:41.239 --> 45:44.575
and my civics teacher.

45:44.576 --> 45:46.577
Well, who threw all those?

45:46.578 --> 45:48.412
Father O'Malley and Rabbi Weisman

45:48.413 --> 45:51.599
are holding a slingshot
for Imam Abdullah.

45:54.252 --> 45:57.337
Well, at least we helped
bring some people together.

45:57.338 --> 46:00.507
Wilsons, if there's a hell,
you're going to it.

46:00.508 --> 46:02.009
Hey, when this is over,

46:02.010 --> 46:04.946
you guys want to walk into a bar?

46:09.976 --> 46:12.895
Oh.

46:12.896 --> 46:15.081
Oh!

46:18.777 --> 46:21.361
I am so full.

46:21.362 --> 46:23.631
I think America is going
to mean death to me.

46:24.949 --> 46:27.785
Funny. That could be the
title of your memoir.

46:27.786 --> 46:31.038
That's a little too
on the nose for me.

46:31.039 --> 46:33.832
I will ask the Wilsons
what they think about it.

46:33.833 --> 46:36.293
The Wilsons!
We've got to save them.

46:36.294 --> 46:38.128
Hassan, we must leave now,

46:38.129 --> 46:41.441
but stealthfully to
avoid detection.

46:44.594 --> 46:45.969
How was your meal, gentlemen?

46:45.970 --> 46:47.805
Oh, it was perfect, so delicious.

46:47.806 --> 46:49.431
But we have to go now.

46:49.432 --> 46:50.724
We're bringing out a new trough

46:50.725 --> 46:52.017
of Butterfinger pieces.

46:52.018 --> 46:54.269
How very fattening of you. Thanks.

46:54.270 --> 46:57.773
Are they freshly crumbled?
You bet ya.

46:57.774 --> 47:00.192
Much as we'd like to gorge
ourselves into an early grave,

47:00.193 --> 47:02.295
we really have to go... now!

47:04.739 --> 47:07.115
Charlie Sheen.

47:07.116 --> 47:08.867
Bush.
Is something wrong?

47:08.868 --> 47:11.161
Oh, no, it's all hunky-dory.

47:11.162 --> 47:12.663
What could be wrong?

47:12.664 --> 47:14.331
We've had our
ridiculously huge dinner,

47:14.332 --> 47:16.208
burped and farted to
our heart's content,

47:16.209 --> 47:19.020
and now we're leaving,
just like any other Americans-

47:21.965 --> 47:23.900
I look so young in that picture.

47:26.344 --> 47:28.679
Holy crap.

47:28.680 --> 47:31.849
Well, it looks like you've got us.

47:31.850 --> 47:33.725
Oh, look, they're putting
out more pizza bread.

47:33.726 --> 47:36.704
Ooh!
Go! Go, go, go, go!

48:00.169 --> 48:02.546
More sprinkles, please.

48:02.547 --> 48:05.400
Oh, and some fresh bread.

48:20.231 --> 48:24.693
Wow. This country
throws out so many cars.

48:24.694 --> 48:26.278
It's fantastic!

48:26.279 --> 48:27.905
I know, right?

48:27.906 --> 48:29.448
This is not good.

48:29.449 --> 48:32.200
The Wilsons need me,
and I've let them down.

48:32.201 --> 48:34.912
The least I can do,
in case we don't make it,

48:34.913 --> 48:37.831
is write a note that clears them.

48:37.832 --> 48:39.249
Can it be?

48:39.250 --> 48:41.752
Hassan, how are you
at building things?

48:41.753 --> 48:43.837
Not as good as blowing things up.

48:43.838 --> 48:45.422
That's going to have to change.

48:45.423 --> 48:48.884
Grab that welding crap
and come with me.

48:48.885 --> 48:52.113
What are we building?
You'll see!

49:00.730 --> 49:02.606
These are hurting my wrists.

49:02.607 --> 49:05.984
Sorry, ma'am. I'm under orders.

49:05.985 --> 49:09.112
All right.

49:09.113 --> 49:10.822
You can do that?

49:10.823 --> 49:12.741
It's highly classified.

49:12.742 --> 49:14.701
So are you.

49:14.702 --> 49:17.037
I'm not sure you know
what that word means,

49:17.038 --> 49:18.973
but thank you.

49:21.209 --> 49:25.229
Ooh, Chris Matthews is going
to get moist over this.

49:27.173 --> 49:29.633
Honey, ain't this the
best anniversary present,

49:29.634 --> 49:31.969
seeing our neighbors go to prison?

49:31.970 --> 49:33.720
Jewelry's nice.

49:33.721 --> 49:35.782
Hey, what song should I play now?

49:37.016 --> 49:39.017
How about America, Eff Yeah,

49:39.018 --> 49:40.852
from that Team America movie?

49:40.853 --> 49:42.854
That song is ironic, Chet.

49:42.855 --> 49:45.583
It ain't ironic if you
don't get the joke.

49:48.528 --> 49:50.112
Ow!

49:50.113 --> 49:51.822
That better be cage-free.

49:51.823 --> 49:55.093
Bite my justice, you
arugula-eating left turd!

49:57.036 --> 49:58.328
Now, I know things look bad,

49:58.329 --> 50:00.122
but we can't just give up.

50:00.123 --> 50:01.915
We have to maintain hope

50:01.916 --> 50:04.918
that something or
someone can save us.

50:04.919 --> 50:06.920
That's right, kids.

50:06.921 --> 50:08.922
We have to hope for
something better

50:08.923 --> 50:10.882
because that's what we do.

50:10.883 --> 50:14.052
I don't know who will help us.
It could be a stranger.

50:14.053 --> 50:16.013
It could be someone who
hasn't been born yet.

50:16.014 --> 50:17.723
It could be-

50:17.724 --> 50:19.182
Flaming skull!

50:19.183 --> 50:20.767
Is that a superhero?

50:20.768 --> 50:23.412
No, it's a flaming skull!

50:27.692 --> 50:30.652
Greetings, infidels!

50:30.653 --> 50:32.362
It's Claude.

50:32.363 --> 50:35.091
My name is Achmed!

50:46.252 --> 50:50.088
Girl car!

50:50.089 --> 50:52.841
Wiener substitute!

50:52.842 --> 50:54.861
Ah, hell, no.

50:57.638 --> 50:59.139
Leave him alone, Chet!

50:59.140 --> 51:01.016
You're what's wrong with America!

51:01.017 --> 51:03.351
No! You're what's
wrong with America!

51:03.352 --> 51:04.644
Americaw!

51:04.645 --> 51:08.690
Gentlemen, you are both correct!

51:08.691 --> 51:11.151
Hey, what the... Get out of my way!

51:11.152 --> 51:12.444
I hate you, Chet!

51:12.445 --> 51:13.737
Damn-
I've always hated you!

51:13.738 --> 51:15.030
Turd car!

51:15.031 --> 51:18.033
Hey.

51:18.034 --> 51:19.451
Oh. Sorry.

51:19.452 --> 51:20.744
No worries.

51:20.745 --> 51:23.789
We've got Obamacare.

51:23.790 --> 51:27.084
Hello, Wilsons! I love you!

51:27.085 --> 51:28.543
Whoa!

51:28.544 --> 51:31.421
Even you, you little backstabber!

51:31.422 --> 51:33.298
Thanks, Achmed.

51:33.299 --> 51:36.301
I still say he's a bad man!

51:36.302 --> 51:39.012
Someone has been practicing!

51:39.013 --> 51:40.781
Thanks!

51:43.226 --> 51:48.688
Great Hoover's pantyhose.
What the hell?

51:48.689 --> 51:50.941
I am turning myself in.

51:50.942 --> 51:52.317
He's turning himself into a bomb.

51:52.318 --> 51:54.778
I think he said,
"Turning myself in."

51:54.779 --> 51:56.822
When did you graduate
from Quantico?

51:56.823 --> 51:58.115
Prepare to fire.

51:58.116 --> 52:01.076
How is it going?

52:01.077 --> 52:02.869
Been better, been worse.

52:02.870 --> 52:06.123
Don't shoot! Please, hear him out.

52:06.124 --> 52:09.876
Ladies and gentlemen
and big dangerous guns,

52:09.877 --> 52:12.671
I came back to tell you that
these wonderful people,

52:12.672 --> 52:16.591
the Wilsons, do not deserve
to be taken to prison.

52:16.592 --> 52:18.718
I do.

52:18.719 --> 52:21.638
Wait, wait, wait.
Why did we all just gasp?

52:21.639 --> 52:23.265
We know he should go to prison.

52:23.266 --> 52:24.558
I don't know.

52:24.559 --> 52:26.268
I feel kind of stupid
about that now.

52:26.269 --> 52:28.061
It's true that I came here

52:28.062 --> 52:29.938
with the intent of doing you harm,

52:29.939 --> 52:31.773
but that is all over.

52:31.774 --> 52:34.401
And the Wilsons had
nothing to do with it

52:34.402 --> 52:36.820
because they are
decent, kind people,

52:36.821 --> 52:39.156
like Americans everywhere.

52:39.157 --> 52:41.158
Let me know when you got the shot.

52:41.159 --> 52:43.201
Roger that.

52:43.202 --> 52:47.122
The Wilsons' only crime
was seeing the best in me,

52:47.123 --> 52:51.001
and my only crime was not
seeing the best in them...

52:51.002 --> 52:54.004
and plotting to blow up the
whole town, yada, yada.

52:54.005 --> 52:55.922
If I may say a word or two.

52:55.923 --> 52:58.842
Of course, sir.
Where's my kill shot, people?

52:58.843 --> 53:00.218
I don't see him.

53:00.219 --> 53:02.512
Oh, wait.

53:02.513 --> 53:04.556
That's better. We're clear.

53:04.557 --> 53:06.433
Subject is in the target zone.

53:06.434 --> 53:08.351
On my command, in three...

53:08.352 --> 53:09.769
I'd like to say a few words

53:09.770 --> 53:12.439
about this remarkable young man.

53:12.440 --> 53:14.941
Hey, whoever is playing
with that laser pen out there

53:14.942 --> 53:16.484
should really stop.

53:16.485 --> 53:18.028
You could detach a retina.

53:18.029 --> 53:19.321
They're going to shoot him.

53:19.322 --> 53:20.906
..Two, one, f-

53:20.907 --> 53:23.200
Sniper team, stand down!

53:23.201 --> 53:24.784
What-
Who is that?

53:24.785 --> 53:26.578
I said stand down!

53:26.579 --> 53:28.705
That is a direct order!

53:28.706 --> 53:30.457
This is General Charles McCarthy

53:30.458 --> 53:32.334
of the United States Joint Command,

53:32.335 --> 53:35.712
and I order you to stand down now!

53:35.713 --> 53:37.130
That's better.

53:37.131 --> 53:39.799
It's a miracle.
Kind of.

53:39.800 --> 53:42.987
Now toss your weapons
in that drainage ditch.

53:45.014 --> 53:47.599
And let Mr. Wilson speak.

53:47.600 --> 53:49.559
Thank you, General McCarthy.

53:49.560 --> 53:51.912
And thank you, son.

53:58.611 --> 54:00.820
Why ain't they shooting him?
He's right there.

54:00.821 --> 54:02.572
He's surrendering peacefully.

54:02.573 --> 54:04.241
Not in my America.

54:04.242 --> 54:05.909
Now, dear, this ain't right.

54:05.910 --> 54:09.513
Why can't you be more
supportive of my hobbies?

54:11.415 --> 54:13.517
That is not good.

54:17.922 --> 54:20.090
I can see my cave from here.

54:20.091 --> 54:23.009
Au revoir, you
towel-headed French fry.

54:23.010 --> 54:26.221
Now, Chet!
Don't "now, Chet" me.

54:26.222 --> 54:28.515
He got what he deserved.

54:28.516 --> 54:30.767
You do good things,
and you'll be rewarded.

54:30.768 --> 54:33.937
You do bad things,
and it's hasta la bye-bye.

54:33.938 --> 54:36.564
Hiya, Chet.

54:36.565 --> 54:38.376
Save me, Sean Hannity!

54:42.071 --> 54:45.365
No! My fuel-efficient hybrid!

54:45.366 --> 54:47.134
My lower torso.

54:59.171 --> 55:01.423
Anyway, you were saying.

55:01.424 --> 55:04.634
How can you still be alive?
I think I know.

55:04.635 --> 55:08.138
Because the American
dream burns within him.

55:08.139 --> 55:10.640
Actually, that's a
piece of shrapnel.

55:10.641 --> 55:12.225
But I feel you.

55:12.226 --> 55:14.811
This amazing young
man, this skeleton-

55:14.812 --> 55:17.647
Yes, I admit now he is
just a talking skeleton.

55:17.648 --> 55:19.983
No offense.
Please. We're past that.

55:19.984 --> 55:21.651
He stays alive

55:21.652 --> 55:25.822
because he believes in the
America we all believe in,

55:25.823 --> 55:28.867
a place where you can
make a fresh start

55:28.868 --> 55:30.744
no matter where you came from,

55:30.745 --> 55:32.829
where you can arrive
in this country

55:32.830 --> 55:34.831
without a dollar in your pocket,

55:34.832 --> 55:37.417
change your name, and
make a new life.

55:37.418 --> 55:40.128
It happened to someone
you might have heard of,

55:40.129 --> 55:43.774
someone named Miss Shania Twain.

55:45.301 --> 55:47.594
She's not American?
Canadian.

55:47.595 --> 55:49.554
No.

55:49.555 --> 55:51.639
Who's Shania Twain?

55:51.640 --> 55:53.892
I love Shania Twain.

55:53.893 --> 55:55.769
You do?

55:55.770 --> 55:59.856
So, to quote one of Shania
Twain's biggest hits-

55:59.857 --> 56:01.399
Man! I Feel Like a Woman!?

56:01.400 --> 56:02.692
No.

56:02.693 --> 56:04.361
Let's find a new spirit

56:04.362 --> 56:06.654
of cooperation and forgiveness.

56:06.655 --> 56:08.156
That Don't Impress Me Much?

56:08.157 --> 56:10.075
Not that one either.
I'm getting there.

56:10.076 --> 56:12.077
Let's put our hearts together and-

56:12.078 --> 56:13.870
Well, those were two
of her biggest hits

56:13.871 --> 56:15.163
according to Billboard's
country-western charts-

56:15.164 --> 56:17.499
Silence!
You were saying?

56:17.500 --> 56:19.876
Let's make a new Americaville

56:19.877 --> 56:25.006
and a new America
from this moment on!

56:25.007 --> 56:27.509
Aw!

56:27.510 --> 56:30.446
Okay, that was big too.

56:33.391 --> 56:36.577
Come here.

56:45.319 --> 56:48.321
I guess there's
nobody for me to hug.

56:48.322 --> 56:51.241
Is this your stupid
little annoying dog?

56:51.242 --> 56:52.826
Billy!
Billy?

56:52.827 --> 56:54.828
I do not know who
you're talking to.

56:54.829 --> 56:56.329
My name is Claude.

56:56.330 --> 56:58.957
No, silly, the dog's name is Bill.

56:58.958 --> 57:01.876
You Americans give
your dogs people names?

57:01.877 --> 57:04.355
You are as dimwitted
as you are boring.

57:06.507 --> 57:09.426
I think I just got
shot with an arrow.

57:09.427 --> 57:11.803
Uh, you can all go home.
Sorry about that.

57:11.804 --> 57:13.179
That's okay.

57:13.180 --> 57:15.181
And Achmed is free
to go too, right?

57:15.182 --> 57:16.474
Uh...

57:16.475 --> 57:18.560
No, I am a criminal after all.

57:18.561 --> 57:20.979
I do not think there
is a Shania Twain song

57:20.980 --> 57:23.565
to help me escape paying
my debt to society.

57:23.566 --> 57:26.109
No One Needs to
Know is appropriate.

57:26.110 --> 57:28.653
Loom

57:28.654 --> 57:31.448
How do you like that?
It's the President!

57:31.449 --> 57:32.866
Of the United States?

57:32.867 --> 57:35.844
Yes, the United
States Motor Company!

57:37.621 --> 57:40.498
Uh, Mr. Achmed,

57:40.499 --> 57:44.544
I've just spoken to the Attorney
General, and based on my offer

57:44.545 --> 57:47.255
to personally vouch for your
renunciation of terrorism

57:47.256 --> 57:50.467
and the fact that you never
accomplished anything destructive...

57:50.468 --> 57:52.218
It's true. He blows.

57:52.219 --> 57:54.387
...our government is
prepared to grant you a full,

57:54.388 --> 57:56.306
complete, and unconditional pardon.

57:56.307 --> 57:58.183
Yay!

57:58.184 --> 58:00.685
On one condition.
Boo!

58:00.686 --> 58:03.354
That you share with me the
plans for that amazing car

58:03.355 --> 58:05.064
that you just drove here today.

58:05.065 --> 58:07.525
My car?

58:07.526 --> 58:10.320
Yes, you've done the
seemingly impossible.

58:10.321 --> 58:12.947
You've created an
American-made automobile

58:12.948 --> 58:16.242
in America that Americans
actually want to buy.

58:16.243 --> 58:18.369
It is a bad-ass ride.

58:18.370 --> 58:20.622
It's a deal.
Yay!

58:20.623 --> 58:22.290
On one condition.

58:22.291 --> 58:23.750
Boo!

58:23.751 --> 58:26.002
No, no, it's a good condition.

58:26.003 --> 58:27.712
Yay!
Yay?

58:27.713 --> 58:29.923
The condition is you give credit

58:29.924 --> 58:33.927
to the man who actually designed
this car, Wayne Wilson.

58:33.928 --> 58:35.637
I thought that looked familiar.

58:35.638 --> 58:37.138
It should.

58:37.139 --> 58:39.516
Hassan and I built it
based on your drawing.

58:39.517 --> 58:41.476
The flaming skull was me.

58:41.477 --> 58:44.604
Hey, everyone, Carl and I are
opening a bed-and-breakfast.

58:44.605 --> 58:45.980
Sorry, Ev.

58:45.981 --> 58:47.815
Well, I wondered
when you were gonna

58:47.816 --> 58:49.359
finally figure yourself out.

58:49.360 --> 58:50.985
Go be happy.

58:50.986 --> 58:53.655
Just leave me and Stan the
beach house in Roanoke.

58:53.656 --> 58:55.657
Stan?
Good-bye!

58:55.658 --> 58:58.576
I was a terrible mayor.

58:58.577 --> 59:01.287
This is the country
you want to live in?

59:01.288 --> 59:03.081
There is not a better one.

59:03.082 --> 59:04.832
Then maybe you can be a reference

59:04.833 --> 59:07.961
for my job application?

59:07.962 --> 59:12.131
Former terrorist log,
love date 8/3/13.

59:12.132 --> 59:14.551
I am now a citizen of Americaville.

59:14.552 --> 59:16.553
It's a good life.

59:16.554 --> 59:20.265
Wayne and Ginny have found
their true calling.

59:20.266 --> 59:24.269
The kids are having fun.

59:24.270 --> 59:26.104
I've found a job where
I can use my skills

59:26.105 --> 59:28.898
and make people happy.

59:28.899 --> 59:31.234
And once a week,
we all get together

59:31.235 --> 59:35.005
for a bountiful feast.

59:38.367 --> 59:42.078
Yes, all in all, it's
been one incredible year,

59:42.079 --> 59:46.499
and the next one
will be even better.

59:46.500 --> 59:49.377
Good night, Wayne.
Good night, Achmed.

59:49.378 --> 59:52.171
Good night, Ginny.
Good night, Achmed.

59:52.172 --> 59:54.132
Good night, Cassidy.
Good night, Kevin.

59:54.133 --> 59:55.550
Good night, little Jeff.

59:55.551 --> 59:57.594
Good night.
Good night!

59:57.595 --> 01:00:00.888
Good night, dog with the
dynamite in his mouth.

01:00:00.889 --> 01:00:02.599
Uh-oh.

01:00:02.600 --> 01:00:04.118
Good boy.

